@startuml
title Swimlane Diagram: Multi-User Interaction Flow

|#AntiqueWhite|Rural Entrepreneur|
start
:Access platform;
:Login to account;
:Submit business idea;
:View AI recommendations;

|#LightBlue|System Backend|
:Authenticate user;
:Retrieve user profile;
:Process AI request;
:Generate recommendations;
:Store results in database;

|#LightGreen|AI Service Layer|
:Receive business context;
:Analyze skills & resources;
:Generate business suggestions;
:Return recommendations;

|#AntiqueWhite|Rural Entrepreneur|
:Review suggestions;

if (Need funding?) then (Yes)
  |#LightCoral|Investor|
  :Browse projects;
  :View entrepreneur profile;
  :Review business plan;
  
  if (Interested?) then (Yes)
    :Contact entrepreneur;
    |#AntiqueWhite|Rural Entrepreneur|
    :Receive investment offer;
    :Discuss terms;
  else (No)
    |#LightCoral|Investor|
    :Continue browsing;
  endif
else (No)
  |#AntiqueWhite|Rural Entrepreneur|
  :Proceed independently;
endif

|#AntiqueWhite|Rural Entrepreneur|
if (Need job opportunities?) then (Yes)
  :Browse job board;
  
  |#LightYellow|Company/NGO|
  :Post job listings;
  :Review applications;
  
  |#LightBlue|System Backend|
  :Match jobs with skills;
  :Send notifications;
  
  |#AntiqueWhite|Rural Entrepreneur|
  :Apply for jobs;
  
  |#LightYellow|Company/NGO|
  :Receive applications;
  :Schedule interviews;
endif

|#AntiqueWhite|Rural Entrepreneur|
if (Need training?) then (Yes)
  :Browse courses;
  
  |#LightBlue|System Backend|
  :Recommend relevant courses;
  :Track progress;
  
  |#AntiqueWhite|Rural Entrepreneur|
  :Enroll in courses;
  :Complete training;
endif

|#AntiqueWhite|Rural Entrepreneur|
:Check government schemes;

|#LightBlue|System Backend|
:Filter eligible schemes;
:Provide scheme details;

|#AntiqueWhite|Rural Entrepreneur|
:Apply for schemes;
:Access application links;

if (Need community support?) then (Yes)
  :Join events;
  :Network with peers;
  
  |#Lavender|NGO|
  :Organize events;
  :Provide mentorship;
  :Share resources;
endif

|#AntiqueWhite|Rural Entrepreneur|
:Implement business plan;
:Track progress;
stop

@enduml
